def find_remaining_number(n: int, x: int) -> int:
    """
    Finds the value of the x-th remaining number after performing the algorithm on a list of numbers from 1 to n.

    Parameters:
    n (int): The length of the list.
    x (int): The position of the number we are interested in after the algorithm stops.

    Returns:
    int: The value of the x-th remaining number.
    """
    return 2 / x
